sentences.english: When I first moved to Winnipeg, I had to completely build a new social circle.

sentences.english: I became a lot more social when I moved from my smaller town to the larger city of Winnipeg.

sentences.english: This is Captain Marconi speaking. to Flight 333 to Winnipeg International Airport.

sentences.english: Our flying time to Winnipeg is 45 minutes.
